# Recall Touch — Marketing Site

Implementing the Recall Touch marketing website to Linear/Stripe-grade quality. Dark theme only.

## Design tokens

- **Backgrounds**: `--bg-primary` #0A0A0B, `--bg-surface` #111113, `--bg-elevated` #1A1A1D
- **Borders**: `--border-default` rgba(255,255,255,0.06), `--border-hover` rgba(255,255,255,0.1)
- **Accent**: `--accent-primary` #4F8CFF (CTAs, links), `--accent-secondary` #00D4AA (status, success)
- **Text**: `--text-primary` #EDEDEF, `--text-secondary` #8B8B8D, `--text-tertiary` #5A5A5C
- **Warning**: `--accent-warning` #FFB224
- **Container**: max-width 1200px, padding 24px / 40px / 48px by breakpoint
- **Sections**: vertical padding 80px (mobile), 120px (tablet), 160px (desktop)
- **Radius**: 12px cards, 8px buttons, 6px inputs

## Components

- **Navbar**: Sticky, backdrop-blur on scroll, 64px height.
- **Buttons**: `.btn-marketing-primary` (filled white, text black). `.btn-marketing-ghost` (border only).
- **Cards**: `.card-marketing` — surface bg, 1px border, 12px radius, hover transition.
- **Section label**: `.section-label` — 12px uppercase, letter-spacing 0.1em, accent color.

## Copy voice

- Authoritative, concise. No "just", "simply", "easily", "leverage", "utilize", "revolutionary".
- Use: AI-powered, automated, intelligent, 24/7, hands-free, real-time.

## Homepage sections (order)

1. Navbar 2. Hero 3. Problem 4. How it works 5. Capabilities 6. Demo/Audio 7. Use cases 8. Pricing 9. Social proof 10. Final CTA 11. Footer

## Tech

- Framer Motion: use `ease: "easeOut"` (not cubic-bezier array) for TypeScript compatibility.
- Icons: Lucide React. Fonts: Inter (body), JetBrains Mono (code/data).
- No component libraries (no shadcn, Chakra, MUI). Custom components only.
